data.description: One-of-a-kind Home! This custom built home has a 28' X 50' RV garage on 8+ acres! Private well! Surrounded by open land. Mountain Views! Animals! Solitude! Fabulous night skies! Your own private oasis in the high desert! Come see the extra large primary suite! It is stunning! 2 50gal hot water tanks! A/C & 500 gal propane tank (owned) for heating, etc. Formal DR with pass thru from kitchen. Split plan. Vaulted ceilings. HOA Gated Community. Adjacent acreage available on N side.
